- `Book_0_LOGOS.pdf` — Foundations & ontology  
- `Book_I_LOGOS.pdf` — Formal development & results  
- `The_Book_of_Life_(Book_II).pdf` — Dynamics and physical grounding  
- `Arrow_of_Time.pdf` — Thermodynamic arrow from continuation conditioning  
- `1_manuscript_main.pdf` — Scale-stratified signatures main manuscript  
- `2_supplementary_information.pdf` — Supplementary information for scale-stratified manuscript  

(Versioned releases are used to ensure stable citation.)

---

## Intended Audience

- Physicists (statistical mechanics, quantum foundations)
- Information theorists
- Researchers in complex systems, emergence, and active inference
- Cognitive scientists and consciousness researchers
- Mathematically inclined readers interested in theoretical unification

The work assumes familiarity with probability, entropy, basic thermodynamics, and related concepts.

